<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>This Privacy Policy outlines how our online drugs store collects, uses, and protects the personal information you provide when you visit or make a purchase from our website. We are committed to safeguarding your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect:</h2>

<p>When you visit our website or place an order, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, payment details, and browsing behavior.</p>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information:</h2>

<p>We use the information we collect to process your orders, communicate with you about your purchases, provide customer support, improve our services, and personalize your shopping experience. We may also use your information to send you promotional emails about new products, special offers, or other updates, but you can opt out of these communications at any time.</p>

<h2>3. Data Security:</h2>

<p>We take the security of your personal information seriously and implement a variety of security measures to protect it from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. We use industry-standard encryption technology to safeguard your data during transmission and store it securely on our servers.</p>

